<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{فَلَا أُقْسِمُ بِالْخُنَّسِ , الْجَوَارِ الْكُنَّسِ , وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا عَسْعَسَ , وَالصُّبْحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٦:</span> الخُنَّسُ: تَخْنِسُ فِي مُجْرَاهَا، تَرْجِعُ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَتَكْنِسُ:</span> تَسْتَتِرُ , كَمَا تَكْنِسُ الظِّبَاءُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ عُمَرُ:</span> <span class="c3">{عَسْعَسَ}</span>: أَدْبَرَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{تَنَفَّسَ}</span>: ارْتَفَعَ النَّهَارُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [التكوير: ١٥ - ١٨]</p> </div>